{"tid":843119,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"黃耀明空位悼Ellen","createTime":"2018-10-01T01:59:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T01:59:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b943ebd31d997a8126fdc4ef5470fb22282e1e7a","tid":843119,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T01:59:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20181001/20511873\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181001%2F20511873&d=IY9ik%2BbGM%2BtiGt2nohrInlzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=c99e885d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181001%2F20511873&h=984e48b2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20181001/20511873</a><br />\n<br />\n黃耀明空位悼Ellen<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181001/large/01ec2p6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181001%2Flarge%2F01ec2p6.jpg&h=a42ef234&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃耀明（左）上周五在台北舉行演唱會，吸引不少台灣觀眾支持。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黃耀明上周五於台北舉行「明曲晚唱」音樂會，明哥因支持雨傘運動被封殺，適逢當日是雨傘運動四周年，他在台上感觸良多︰「這是一個思想容易犯罪的年代，雖然我們年紀大的人沒留給下一代比較公平的世界，但我們可以透過詩歌、文字、繪畫等等將公平正義的想法流傳。」<br />\n<br />\n明哥好友盧凱彤（Ellen）原本會在演唱會出現，可惜8月不幸墮樓身亡，明哥亦在台上留下一個空蕩蕩的位置給Ellen。明哥最後的encore更是Ellen愛曲《美麗在心頭》，他哽咽說：「別多說了，沒甚麼好說，就用音樂記得她，她寫的文字、她的結他和音樂，都在我們之中。」<br />\n<br />\n撰文︰祖李  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n譚耀文膺最有價值演員<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n劉美娟親自配票阻黃牛"}]}